  {
   "kind": 1,
   "value": "### 5. Linter de Einstein (Detección de Errores)\n\nFuerza un error de índice repetido 3 veces para confirmar que el Linter dispara su alerta roja.",
   "languageId": "markdown",
   "outputs": [],
   "metadata": {}
  },
  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "FastTensor[vecA[mu]]; SetDisplayName[vecA, \"A\"];\nFastTensor[vecB[-mu]]; SetDisplayName[vecB, \"B\"];\nFastTensor[vecC[mu]]; SetDisplayName[vecC, \"C\"];\n\nexpr5 = vecA[mu] * vecB[-mu] * vecC[mu];\nPrint[\"Output (Linter de expresion con 3 indices mu): \"];\nCheckEinsteinNotation[expr5];",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [
    {
     "items": [
      {
       "data": "<div class=\"wl-print-output\"><div class=\"wl-print-line\"><span class=\"wl-ps\">** </span><div class=\"vscode-wolfram-wllatex-prerendered wl-lb-pending\" data-lb-id=\"lb-mrp1sb2f-wotj1r6\" data-page-width-em=\"50\" data-latex-b64=\"XG1hdGhybXtEZWZUZW5zb3J9\" style=\"opacity:0.65;transition:opacity 0.35s\"><div class=\"wl-lb-content\"><span class=\"katex-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6944em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathrm\">DefTensor</span></span></span></span></span></span></div></div><span class=\"wl-ps\">: Defining </span><span class=\"wl-ps\">tensor </span><div class=\"vscode-wolfram-wllatex-prerendered wl-lb-pending\" data-lb-id=\"lb-mrp1sb2h-tyrwf6j\" data-page-width-em=\"50\" data-latex-b64=\"XG1hdGhybXt2ZWNBfVxsZWZ0KFxtYXRocm17bXV9XHJpZ2h0KQ==\" style=\"opacity:0.65;transition:opacity 0.35s\"><div class=\"wl-lb-content\"><span class=\"katex-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathrm\">vecA</span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"minner\"><span class=\"mopen delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">(</span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathrm\">mu</span></span><span class=\"mclose delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">)</span></span></span></span></span></span></div></div><span class=\"wl-ps\">. </span><span class=\"wl-ps\"></span></div></div>",
